page.title: 16FAMILY LIFE
page.content: On a Sunday, we go to my grandfathers and spend the day there, telling the latest gossip. We come home at about 3.30pm. There are seven people in my family, my mum,my dad,a brother, a sister I also have a step sister.My other sister lives in Australia. On Thursday we we go to visit my aunty Sharon who is divorced, she has a boy-friend called Steven,he is nice ,we all like him.Aunty Sharon has two daughters,one is called Kelly who is four years old and Gemma who is two and a half years old.She also has a son called Dean who is one.
